Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlockingBuffer
    The BlockingBuffer acts as a shared location between filters.
    FrameBuilder
    The FrameBuilder class is a Filter that gets an input sequence from ReverseComplementor and outputs a frame or subsequence of 3 bases to go to the Translator
    GapFinder
    The GapFinder class is a Filter that sends all of the sequences of bases separated.
    OpenReadingFrameFilter
    An Open Reading Frame Filter is what the entire program is, but for the class with the same name it just acts as a controller.
    ORFFinder
    This class is the final Filter and it finds the Open Reading Frames, the ORFs are found by waiting until a stop codon and if the sequence made before that codon is over 21 than it is an ORF.
    ReverseComplementor
    The ReverseComplementor reverses the sequence from GapFinder and switches all of the sequence to its complements.
    Translator
    The Translator filter takes the frames from the FrameBuilder and translates them into a Codon.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Codon
    The Codon enumeration is used for the transcription from DNA to RNA
